title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Talent requires practice to reach its full potential. You might instinctively use untapped expertise today thats likely been long forgotten. Colleagues or friends might be pleasantly surprised, and you may be perplexed as to why you ever let this skill fall by the wayside. Focus more attention on these underdeveloped gifts while knowledgeable Mercury rises to the challenge in your 6th House of Details, but don't put in the work unless you truly wish to grow. Educator Carol Dweck wrote, Its not how good you are. Its how good you want to be. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
